All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable
public class SecureBoxException
extends javacard.framework.CardRuntimeException

Exception class that is used by SecureBox implementation to indicate invalid usage. If this exception gets caught, the provided reason code will give an indication about the error occurred.

See Also:
